{
  "text": "And we have crusaders from Orion coming to this planet for mind control purposes. How do they do this? As all they follow the law of one observing free will. Contact is made with those who call those then upon the planetary sphere act much as do you disseminate the attitudes and philosophy of their particular understanding of the law of one, which is a service to self. These become the elite. Through these the attempt begins to create a condition whereby the remainder of the planetary entities are enslaved by their own free will.",
